ENTRY       EC 1.3.3.9                  Enzyme
NAME        secologanin synthase
CLASS       Oxidoreductases;
            Acting on the CH-CH group of donors;
            With oxygen as acceptor
SYSNAME     loganin:oxygen oxidoreductase (ring-cleaving)
REACTION    loganin + NADPH + H+ + O2 = secologanin + NADP+ + 2 H2O [RN:R03555]
ALL_REAC    R03555;
            (other) R05833
SUBSTRATE   loganin [CPD:C01433];
            NADPH [CPD:C00005];
            H+ [CPD:C00080];
            O2 [CPD:C00007]
PRODUCT     secologanin [CPD:C01852];
            NADP+ [CPD:C00006];
            H2O [CPD:C00001]
COMMENT     A heme-thiolate protein (P-450). Secologanin is the precursor of the monoterpenoid indole alkaloids and ipecac alkaloids.
HISTORY     EC 1.3.3.9 created 2002
